chrome.notes: When `self-x-end` is used as a single keyword, or alongside `span-all`, it unexpectedly allows the anchored box to overflow the viewport, obscuring content. Use `place-self: anchor-center` as a workaround. See [bug 438334710](https://crbug.com/438334710).
